    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Maintenance for off-road driving"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Whenever you drive off-road through sand, mud or water, more frequent maintenance may be required of the following items:\n\u2022 Brake pads and rotors\n\u2022 Brake lining and drums\n\u2022 Brake lines and hoses\n\u2022 Wheel bearing grease\n\u2022 Differential, transfer gear oil and automatic transmission fluid\n\u2022 Differential gear oil and CVT fluid\n\u2022 Steering linkage\n\u2022 Propeller shaft and front drive shaft\n\u2022 Air cleaner filter\n\u2022 Clutch housing (check water entry)",
      "style": "normal"
    }
  ],
